Package io.smudgr.util.output

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FrameOutput
    The FrameOutput interface defines methods for interacting with an output stream of an arbitrary format.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnimatedGifEncoder
    Class AnimatedGifEncoder - Encodes a GIF file consisting of one or more frames.
    GifOutput
    The GifOutput output stream records an animated GIF at this ideal GIF frame rate.
    ImageOutput
    The ImageOutput stream records a single PNG file for every frame added.
